WEBVTT

00:07:29.333 --> 00:07:31.101
we had at that time,

00:07:31.125 --> 00:07:35.018
which were Henry Spira,
head of Animal Rights International,

00:07:35.042 --> 00:07:36.643
and Peter Singer,

00:07:36.667 --> 00:07:38.684
who wrote the book "Animal Liberation,"

00:07:38.708 --> 00:07:42.250
which is considered the modern treatise
about animal rights.

00:07:43.208 --> 00:07:45.184
You know, I read Peter's book to prepare,

00:07:45.208 --> 00:07:47.226
I tried to get into his mindset,

00:07:47.250 --> 00:07:48.893
and I have to admit, it was tough,

00:07:48.917 --> 00:07:50.976
I'm not becoming a vegan,

00:07:51.000 --> 00:07:53.518
my company wasn't going that way.

00:07:53.542 --> 00:07:55.893
But I really thought we could learn a lot.

00:07:55.917 --> 00:07:58.893
And so I set up a breakfast meeting
in New York City.

00:07:58.917 --> 00:08:01.143
And I remember sitting down,
getting ready,